Package uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.machine.tags

Class IPTag

java.lang.Object
uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.machine.tags.Tag
uk.ac.manchester.spinnaker.machine.tags.IPTag
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<Tag>
public final class IPTag extends Tag
Used to hold data that is contained within an IP tag. IP tags allow data to flow at runtime from SpiNNaker to the outside world via UDP packets. Those UDP packets may have an SDP header, or that may be removed; this is one of the configuration options for the tag.
